SDMMC004_CSDV2Type Struct Reference

Detailed Description

This structure stores the SD v2 card's Csd register content.

uint32_t SDMMC004_CSDV2Type::WriteSpeedFactor

This field is fixed to 2h, which indicates 4 multiples. Write timeout can be calculated by multiplying the read access time and R2W_FACTOR.
